# Track ONLY the slide research/update task definitions.
# Everything else under Scheduled/ (personal digests, generated output,
# the separately-versioned slide-updater repo, sample data) stays untracked.

# 1. Ignore everything at the top level by default.
/*

# 2. Re-include the two slide task folders and this gitignore.
!slide-research-all/
!slide-update-all/
!.gitignore

# 3. Inside those folders, ignore everything except the SKILL.md definition.
slide-research-all/*
!slide-research-all/SKILL.md
slide-update-all/*
!slide-update-all/SKILL.md
